3.5. Eﬀect of EOCL on normal rectal temperature of mice

signiﬁcant (p < 0.05) decrease in rectal temperature at 30 and 60 min
post-treatment. Diazepam, 1 mg/kg, i.p., only caused signiﬁcant
(p < 0.05) reduction in rectal temperature at 60 min post treatment
